<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset='utf-8' />
    <title>Email</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>Dear {{name}},</p>

    <p>Greetings from Ujjwal Finserv Private Limited.</p>

    {{#if isPaid}}
      <p>Your payment for {{type}} has been received successfully.</p>
      <p>This is to confirm we received ₹{{feeAmount}}
        towards your
        {{type}}
        fees for loan application
        {{applicationNo}}.</p>
      <p>Please find the attached paid {{type}} invoice for your reference.</p>
    {{else}}
      <p>Your loan application
        <strong>{{applicationNo}}</strong>
        for Personal Loan of ₹{{amount}}
        has been approved.</p>
      <p>Your interest rate is
        <strong>{{interestRate}}%</strong>
        per annum and EMI is ₹{{emi}}
        for a tenure of
        {{tenure}}
        months.</p>
      <p>Please find your
        {{type}}
        letter attached. Kindly pay the
        {{type}}
        fee of ₹{{feeAmount}}.</p>
    {{/if}}

    <p>Thank you for choosing Ujjwal Finserv.</p>

    <br />
    <p>Regards,</p>
    <p>Ujjwal Finserv<br />
      Loan Specialist<br />
      +91-{{employeePhone}}<br />
      Email: info@testmail.com<br />
      Website: https://papayawhip-woodcock-558791.hostingersite.com/<br />
      Office: test address</p>
  </body>
</html>